{"tid":719642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【趕絕基層人口】北京再趕人！維穩辦設限期 逾期不遷強行驅離!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2018-06-27T14:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T17:12:10.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"196f78c841a46a179cce9ac6953b1f5148745ab7","tid":719642,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T14:48:53.000Z","msg":"北京市政府去年一度強行將住在市郊、分租房屋的<span style=\"color: red;\">基層</span>人口趕走，原以為行動已經結束，但北京市昌平區維穩辦、綜合治理辦前日發出緊急通知，指「配合首都人口疏散工作」，限住在大院、廠房、非本地居民住宅分租房者，要在下月3月前自行離開，逾期仍不離開者，「各村組統人員強行驅離」，當局的行動被網民批評是「趕人2.0」。<br />\n<br />\n有關通告在網上瘋傳，內容列明，僅批准北京本地居民在合法住宅地上自住的房屋，才可以分租給別人居住，其他類型的分租房，都不得住人。<br />\n對於當局突然再驅趕<span style=\"color: red;\">基層</span>人口，不少網民都批評這根本是歧視：「如果有范ＸＸ的收入，會租這種地方？」「主要是高樓大廈房租貴......」<br />\n北京大興區去年11月發生奪命大火，造成19死8傷，事後當局大舉將基層人口趕走，引發民怨。今年1月當局統計，全市的人口減少2.2萬人，是自2000年以來首度出現負增長。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180627/large/1530094013_6695.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180627%2Flarge%2F1530094013_6695.jpg&h=be93a013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180627/58370348\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180627%2F58370348&d=GsfHRPUiUDhQ0xnCOYShs49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=f0d09607\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180627%2F58370348&h=720e81f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180627/58370348</a>"},{"pid":"cf5bf3405519cf9ddbddc61959f8a1ec53c9434c","tid":719642,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T14:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ffc77701399d5988384845a40fcdb7b969fc32","tid":719642,"uid":56999,"like":0,